overview: "Jasil Brazz" is a filmed performance of Herbie Mann and his jazz ensemble which has never before been released on home video.  Featured band members include Herbie Mann on flute, Marc Cohen on keyboards, Paul Socolow on bass, Romero Lubambo on guitar, Ricky Sebastian on drums and Cyro Baptista on percussion.
title: Herbie Mann: Jasil Brazz
